INPUT
STORE Y
Skipcond 800 /if (y < 0)
JUMP PRINT_NEG
Skipcond 000 /if (y > 0)
JUMP PRINT_POS
Skipcond 200 /if (y = 0)
JUMP PRINT_POS
HALT

/ Subroutines
PRINT_POS,  LOAD POSITIVE / onto ACCUMULATOR
			OUTPUT
            HALT
            
PRINT_NEG,  LOAD NEGATIVE / onto ACCUMILATOR
			OUTPUT
            HALT
            
PRINT_ZERO, LOAD ZERO     / onto ACCUMILATOR
			OUTPUT
            HALT
			







/Variables
Y, 		  DEC  0
NEGATIVE, DEC -1
POSITIVE, DEC  1
ZERO,     DEC  0